  <summary>6/6/2000--Introduced.
Urges the United Nations (UN) to establish a permanent standing UN security force of up to 15,000 volunteers who are trained and equipped for rapid deployment for not to exceed six months in international peacekeeping operations pursuant to a UN Security Council resolution.</summary>
